  {
    "client_msg_id": "6ee4c89d-2665-4f62-8162-8b3761abc4d7",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "It has very little to do with the tactility of it. That's part of it, sure, but that's like saying the big advancement of the iPhone over what came before is that the iPhone has a good touchscreen. In fact, the iPhone was a computer than travelled with you. It was an augmentation of your person. Dynamicland is an augmentation of your environment.",
